    <tags>react, frontend, ai, error-handling, telemetry</tags>
    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Code implementation extending the 034 hook + component with error/empty handling. Touches AI rate-limit surface (ADR-016), error telemetry boundary (FR-24, error-only), and FR-16 / NFR-11 UX contract. FULL rigor — code-review + adr-check at Step 9.5 because the failure paths are user-visible and the telemetry is load-bearing for monitoring.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>C</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
